<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idc2e69793-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The date of the enactment of this section, referred to in subsec. (b)(2), is the date of enactment of <ref href="/us/pl/106/117">Pub. L. 106–117</ref>, which was approved <date date="1999-11-30">Nov. 30, 1999</date>.</p>
